room_title: Escape room "Corporate Rage" by Clueless Escape Rooms in Ann Arbor
review: We had a great time! We did Corporate Rage, very different premise but was lots of fun!

room_title: Escape room "Corporate Rage" by Clueless Escape Rooms in Ann Arbor
review: We did the Corporate Rage room as a work outing, there were 7 of us total. We made it out with 29 seconds to spare! It was a lot of fun and had different electronic elements which were very cool and unlike other escape rooms. We will definitely be back again to do the other room!

room_title: Escape room "Corporate Rage" by Clueless Escape Rooms in Ann Arbor
review: We did the Corporate room and had a lot of fun. We didn't escape but still loved it. Both of the owners were great and gave us a lot of good ideas for our next escape room adventure. Can't wait to head back especially for the new rooms!
